retweeted_text: Wondering how you can help keep your friends healthy this summer? Stay safe from #COVID19: Wash your hands, stay 6 feet apart, and #WearAMask.  Learn more about how you and your friends can help protect each other: https://t.co/l3eipKjvjF. #MaskingForAFriend #WorldMaskWeek https://t.co/czZC6J2oNi

full_text:
Testing is a critical tool as we continue to defeat this virus. The #CARESAct has helped Georgia quickly expand its testing capacity and test as many people as possible.

Find a list of test sites here: https://t.co/kySvzVwWQE https://t.co/dpGZq45IfX

✔️Reaches above nose & below chin, completely covering mouth & nostrils
✔️Fits snugly against sides of your face
✔️Is made of multiple layers of cloth that you can breathe through

Jobs are being lost.

But Senate Democrats are choosing to use this moment as political leverage. Absolutely pathetic.
